---
title: Panko Crusted Chicken Breast with sweet potato champ mash
description: Champ is a traditional Irish dish but in this recipe it's made with a twist, using sweet potatoes instead of the more commonly used potato. The jazzed-up champ accompanies crispy coated chicken and a crisp salad for a colourful, nutritious and tasty plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W46_IE_IECC31221-6_Main_high-754e59b3.jpg
